          },
          "reviewBody": "Pathways School Gurgaon is a place where educators and students alike are given room to grow, explore, attempt new things and wings to soar, no holds barred. The positive work ethics and global exposure is unique. The clean, safe, fun, learner friendly, beautiful learning spaces and avant-garde school culture makes it the benchmark of IB schools in Asia.",
