        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Pathways School - Baliawas"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Vandana Vishwakarma"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-07-17",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I had been associated with pathways for a long time as a DP faculty member and now the parent of two children studying in Pathways school Gurugram . One of the best school ,which gives you the right  environment ,experience and learning of an IB school. The student here are exposed to multiple opportunities with no dearth of the resources provided by the school (by the way no school in north India Provides the facilty and resources of that level) . The school facilitates students to excels beyond academics as per their stengths . The way ,Pathways implement the standards and practices of a true IB School , I can vouch No school in north India can beat the competence level of the implementation. A great learning centre for both the faculty members and students .The perks and the privelages the school provides to their employee (both existing and moved on) is  appreciable.Worth it ! Must experience . I wish all the best to the school to keep flourishing ,and growing its brand identity.\n\nEx -faculty member and pathways parent",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Pathways School - Baliawas"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Sukhwinder kaur"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-04-27",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Pathways School Gurgaon is such a learning centre that give wings to its students to explore their creativity and talent. Sky is the limit for them….the students are raised with great confidence and courage.\nThe entire school community is very approachable be it teachers, principal, or director. The school is very open to feedback for the well-being of its students.\nThe school believes every child is different and there are numerous opportunities for students to showcase their creativity and talent through various events and exhibitions that happen throughout the year.\nNot to mention, it’s an inclusive school and believes every child has a right to quality education.\nA very happy parent, I have seen wholesome development of my child who thinks out of the box and comes up with such queries that amazes us.\nMay the school keeps on doing the wonderful work of imparting education that’s not just limited to classrooms.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Pathways School - Baliawas"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Monika Jolly"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-04-26",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Pathways is an excellent School and we are very satisfied and happy  parents. The school gave our  daughter freedom of voice and choice  which has helped her shape up into a confident girl. We would like to  recommend this school to other parents.\nRegards\nMonika Jolly\nMother of Anoushka Jolly",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
