            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Great place to be a part of. Especially during the time of the pandemic, the entire Community looked after each other. We ensured food and medical supplies were delivered to the ones in need, everyone got paid on time and ensured people return safely to the school. Vaccination drive was conducted for all of our support staff and was even extended to their family members",
